note:
<Custom React Effect>
// Check if the action healed the target.
if (this.isHpEffect() && value < 0) {
  // Check if the target is on the same team as the original caster of the state.
  if (target.isActor() === origin.isActor()) {
    // If it is, increase the healing done by 200%.
    value = Math.ceil(value * 2);
  // If the target and original caster are on opposite teams...
  } else {
    // Nullify the heal.
    value = 0;
  }
}
</Custom React Effect>
